DATABASE SCHEMA — create these tables in Supabase
─────────────────────────────────────────────────

Table: print_jobs
  id                UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
  pickup_code       TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL  -- e.g. "PRN-4K7X"
  customer_name     TEXT NOT NULL
  customer_phone    TEXT NOT NULL         -- encrypted (AES-256 via PII_ENCRYPTION_KEY)
  file_name         TEXT NOT NULL         -- original filename shown to customer
  file_path         TEXT NOT NULL         -- Supabase Storage path (private)
  file_type         TEXT NOT NULL         -- 'pdf' | 'docx' | 'image'
  page_count        INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 1
  copies            INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 1
  colour_mode       TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'bw'    -- 'bw' | 'colour'
  sides             TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'single' -- 'single' | 'double'
  paper_size        TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'a4'     -- 'a4' | 'a3' | 'letter'
  price_per_page    NUMERIC(6,2) NOT NULL
  total_amount      NUMERIC(8,2) NOT NULL
  status            TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'PENDING_PAYMENT'
                    -- PENDING_PAYMENT → PAID → PRINTING → 
                    -- READY → COLLECTED → CANCELLED
  razorpay_order_id TEXT
  razorpay_payment_id TEXT
  created_at        TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
  paid_at           TIMESTAMPTZ
  printed_at        TIMESTAMPTZ
  collected_at      TIMESTAMPTZ
  agent_version     TEXT  -- which agent version printed this job
  error_log         TEXT  -- if printing failed, store reason here

Table: print_pricing
  id              UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
  colour_mode     TEXT NOT NULL  -- 'bw' | 'colour'
  sides           TEXT NOT NULL  -- 'single' | 'double'
  paper_size      TEXT NOT NULL  -- 'a4' | 'a3' | 'letter'
  price_per_page  NUMERIC(6,2) NOT NULL
  is_active       BOOLEAN DEFAULT true
  updated_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

Seed print_pricing with sensible Indian market rates:
  B&W   + Single + A4     = ₹2.00/page
  B&W   + Double + A4     = ₹1.50/page
  Colour + Single + A4    = ₹10.00/page
  Colour + Double + A4    = ₹8.00/page
  B&W   + Single + A3     = ₹4.00/page
  Colour + Single + A3    = ₹18.00/page
  B&W   + Single + Letter = ₹2.00/page
  Colour + Single + Letter= ₹10.00/page

RLS Policies:
  print_jobs:    Customers can INSERT their own row (status check)
                 SELECT only where pickup_code matches (for tracking)
                 Admin (authenticated) can SELECT/UPDATE all rows
  print_pricing: Public SELECT (everyone can read prices)
                 Admin only can INSERT/UPDATE

