SUPABASE STORAGE
─────────────────────────────────────────────────

Bucket name: print-files
  Access: PRIVATE (never public)
  Max file size: 25MB
  Allowed MIME types:
    application/pdf
    application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document
    image/jpeg
